local this = UIComponent(Address)
function ShowMenu(name) for i = 0, this:ChildCount() - 1 do local child = UIComponent(this:Find(i)) child:SetVisible(child:Id() == name) end end

uientry.unicode: This shows the number of players in the alliance and the maximum number allowed.

uientry.s:
function OnSelect() local this = UIComponent(Address) local team = UIComponent(this:Parent(4))
team:LuaCall("KickPlayer", this:Parent()) end

local parent = UIComponent(UIComponent(Address):Parent(3))
function OnSelect() parent:LuaCall("SelectOption", Address) end

function OnSelect() local this = UIComponent(Address)
if this:CurrentState() ~= "inactive" then local panel = UIComponent(this:Parent("main_panel")) panel:LuaCall("AddToTeam", 1) end end

function OnSelect() local parent = UIComponent(UIComponent(Address):Parent("main_panel"))
parent:LuaCall("SwapSelectedPlayer") end
